text: Rénelle Lamote (born 26 December 1993, in Coulommiers) is a French middle- distance runner. ==Career== She was born to an Ivorian mother and a French father. She specialises in the 800 metres. She represented her country at the 2014 European Championships and 2015 European Indoor Championships reaching the semifinals on both occasions.
